English template — TODO

Translate the entire `template/pt-br/_shared/` and `template/pt-br/_presets/`
trees to English. The CLI does not yet expose `--lang en` because this slot
is empty.

Source of truth: `template/pt-br/_shared/CLAUDE.md` and the four presets
under `template/pt-br/_presets/`. When translating:

- Filenames already in English — keep them.
- Frontmatter keys already in English — keep them.
- Translate frontmatter values, headings, prose, slash-command bodies,
  CLAUDE.md and README.md.
- Update the CLI in `bin/cli.mjs` to accept and route `--lang en`.

Until then, the CLI assumes `pt-br` and copies from `template/pt-br/`.
